\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ra.\">Ra.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">269</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: abs., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">παραβαλοῦ</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg009.perseus-grc1:180\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">180</biblScope> </bibl>: metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">παραβάλλου λοιδορῶν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">avast</tr_> with your abuse! <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.711d</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"IV\" id=\"n77768.10\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">throw, turn, bend sideways</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄμμα π. θύννου δίκην</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cast</tr_> it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">askance</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg008:308\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">308</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸν ὀφθαλμὸν παράβαλλ᾽ ἐς Καρίαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg002.perseus-grc1:173\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.\">Eq.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">173</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὠφθαλμὼ παραβάλλεις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:362\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><