\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.87</biblScope> </bibl> (<xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.l.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">περιβ-</ref> </xr>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">; π. τοὺς γομφίους</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lay to</tr_> one's grinders, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg005.perseus-grc1:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pax\">Pax</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">34</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. τὸ θύριον τοῦ λόγου</foreign>, metaph., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">put to</tr_> the door . . , <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">close</tr_> it, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.94</biblScope> </bibl> of. </sense> <sense n=\"V\" id=\"n77768.11\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">deposit with</tr_> one, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">entrust to</tr_> him, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τινί τι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:154\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.154</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"VI\" id=\"n77768.12\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">deceive, betray</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001